4Geeks Academy offers a 16-week course to become an AI Machine Learning Engineer. The course is designed for beginners and helps students start a career as a data scientist, building their first machine learning models. The instructors include Sayyed Nezhadi, a PhD in Artificial Intelligence, Francesco Pugliese, a PhD in Robotics & Artificial Intelligence, and Manuel Mena, a Senior Data Scientist. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and teaches students to create predictive models using powerful libraries like Pandas and Numpy. Students also work on real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The course is available in English and Spanish. More information can be found at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop